# Changelog

## 1.0.0 - 2023-02-19
- Support for Laravel Nova 4
- Added option to set image preview width
- Reduced script size: 5.5 KiB
- Removed logging
- Require at least Node.js 12
- Require PHP 7.4 or above

## 0.0.2 - 2020-07-31

- Made image field optional (closed [#1](https://github.com/CaddyDz/NovaPreviewResource/issues/1) thanks to Oleksandr Roskovynskyi)
